1
00:00:02,381 --> 00:00:04,450
What kind of script is this?

2
00:00:04,637 --> 00:00:05,238
If you like someone,

3
00:00:05,239 --> 00:00:06,406
why not just say it?

4
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:09,609
It makes me look like I'm heartless.

5
00:00:16,483 --> 00:00:17,649
I found that recording

6
00:00:17,650 --> 00:00:18,650
of your confession.

7
00:00:19,686 --> 00:00:21,321
Why didn't you just tell me?

8
00:00:22,522 --> 00:00:24,024
Who gave you the right to decide?

9
00:00:32,365 --> 00:00:33,432
What about the ending?

10
00:00:33,433 --> 00:00:34,701
Why is the last page missing?

11
00:00:36,229 --> 00:00:37,229
Thank you

12
00:00:37,270 --> 00:00:38,971
for sharing your thoughts on the story.

13
00:00:38,972 --> 00:00:40,006
The director wants

14
00:00:40,473 --> 00:00:41,707
the final ending

15
00:00:41,708 --> 00:00:42,748
to be left up to you guys.

16
00:00:43,610 --> 00:00:44,477
Thanks, Director.

17
00:00:44,478 --> 00:00:45,912
I'll let Bai Xing know.

18
00:00:55,021 --> 00:00:56,222
Hey, Hei Yan.

19
00:00:56,856 --> 00:00:57,824
About that script...

20
00:00:57,825 --> 00:00:59,525
why is there no ending?

21
00:00:59,526 --> 00:01:00,526
Because there isn't one.

22
00:01:01,461 --> 00:01:02,461
What do you mean?

23
00:01:02,829 --> 00:01:04,263
I'll tell you next time we meet.

24
00:01:04,264 --> 00:01:05,064
Next time?

25
00:01:05,064 --> 00:01:05,965
No way.

26
00:01:05,965 --> 00:01:06,566
Wait for me.

27
00:01:06,567 --> 00:01:07,767
I'm coming over to your place.

28
00:01:08,268 --> 00:01:08,835
It's so late.

29
00:01:08,836 --> 00:01:10,476
It's not like you go to bed early anyway.

30
00:01:14,874 --> 00:01:15,375
Hey.

31
00:01:15,376 --> 00:01:16,643
What's your address?

32
00:01:23,450 --> 00:01:24,810
Are you sneaking over for a tryst?

33
00:01:26,186 --> 00:01:28,146
I'm just worried about
being caught by paparazzi.

34
00:01:35,895 --> 00:01:37,063
Do you live alone?

35
00:01:40,033 --> 00:01:41,134
And if I don't?

36
00:01:41,401 --> 00:01:43,336
Isn't it a bit late
to be asking that now?

37
00:01:47,974 --> 00:01:48,974
Anyway,

38
00:01:49,442 --> 00:01:50,043
about that short film...

39
00:01:50,044 --> 00:01:51,244
why doesn't it have an ending?

40
00:01:52,512 --> 00:01:53,413
The director said

41
00:01:53,414 --> 00:01:54,614
he wants us to discuss it.

42
00:01:55,448 --> 00:01:56,448
Discuss it?

43
00:01:57,984 --> 00:01:58,852
I'm the type of person who

44
00:01:58,853 --> 00:02:00,533
skips straight to the last page of a book.

45
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,389
How am I supposed to deal with no ending?

46
00:02:08,628 --> 00:02:09,828
You're playing the guy

47
00:02:09,829 --> 00:02:11,669
with a secret crush
on his best friend, right?

48
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:15,300
The one who's so good to me,

49
00:02:15,301 --> 00:02:15,969
but then I

50
00:02:15,970 --> 00:02:17,603
get a girlfriend,

51
00:02:17,604 --> 00:02:18,438
so he leaves

52
00:02:18,438 --> 00:02:19,205
a voice memo he never

53
00:02:19,206 --> 00:02:20,672
intended for me to hear

54
00:02:20,673 --> 00:02:22,175
and then just moves abroad?

55
00:02:24,844 --> 00:02:26,613
Stop just saying "mm."

56
00:02:27,013 --> 00:02:27,547
Don't you have

57
00:02:27,548 --> 00:02:28,788
any thoughts on your character?

58
00:02:29,983 --> 00:02:30,983
It's just acting.

59
00:02:30,984 --> 00:02:31,851
As long as it's believable.

60
00:02:31,852 --> 00:02:33,219
It's not believable!

61
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:36,589
If you like someone,
you should just say it.
